products.title: Ribbons Solar White Pleated Skylight Blind
products.description: Ribbons solar, a very affordable and quality blinds perfect for any home, there are many beautiful colours to choose from. Featuring an aluminium coated back, this fabric reflects heat in summer and retains heat in summer. A perfect thermal fabric. Product id: db-pls0133 fabric colour: white material: 100% polyester headrail: white rails and hardware with pull down tab and visible guide wires to support the blind fabric.
